MultiTex - Class in slickshader
Class to support the concept of a single artifact being comprised of multiple image resources.
For example a colourmap, normalmap, diffusemap, and specularmap.
MultiTex(List<String>) - Constructor for class slickshader.MultiTex
Constructs a new MultiTex object using the textures identified in textures.
The index of the textures in the list will be the texture unit that the texture is bound to.
